      "description": "$19,950 - Honest fair-condition vehicle that shows the kind of cosmetic wear, age-related blemishes, and general imperfections you would expect from a driver rather than a show car. It presents decently overall but is not mint, with visible flaws inside and out that a careful buyer will notice. That said, it remains a solid, usable example for someone who wants an affordable entry point and is comfortable with a vehicle that has clearly been used and enjoyed.",
