      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 44
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Honest little project car with plenty of life left for the right buyer. It\u2019s not perfect, but it\u2019s an affordable way to get into a vehicle you can tinker with, use for parts, or turn into a dependable budget ride. If you like getting your hands dirty and want something with potential at a fair price, this could be a great fit. Priced to move and ready for its next chapter.",
      "price": 3900.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 44
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Strong-running project with a willing drivetrain, solid oil pressure, and a transmission that pulls through the gears the way it should. Not a showroom car, but it\u2019s an honest, usable platform with good bones for someone who appreciates mechanical simplicity and easy wrenchability. Starts, moves, and stops, with the kind of character you expect from a driver-grade example that still has plenty of life left for commuting, tinkering, or building into something better. Priced for the enthusiast who sees potential instead of cosmetics.",
      "price": 7900.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 44
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Runs. Drives. Cheap way into a car. Not pretty, but it gets the job done. Priced to move fast.",
      "price": 4900.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 44
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This car has the kind of weathered, hard-earned presence that turns heads for all the right reasons\u2014a true diamond-in-the-rough with loads of personality. It\u2019s the sort of machine that invites a creative owner to bring their vision to life, whether you\u2019re after a budget-friendly daily with character, a hands-on weekend project, or a distinctive ride with old-school soul. There\u2019s a raw honesty to it that\u2019s getting harder to find, and for the right buyer, that makes it far more interesting than something sterile and forgettable.",
      "price": 5200.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 44
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
