    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Budget-friendly and priced to move. This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s an honest old runner with plenty of life left for the right buyer. Great option if you need cheap wheels, a project, or something to tinker with. If you\u2019re after a showroom car, this isn\u2019t it\u2014but if you want straightforward value and don\u2019t mind a bit of TLC, it could be a really handy buy. Come have a look and see if it suits what you need.",
      "price": 3900.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 44
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Clean, straightforward budget ride with solid bones and plenty of usable life left for the next owner. It shows age cosmetically and is being sold in as-is condition, but it still offers a strong value for someone who wants affordable transportation or a practical project platform. The powertrain pulls well for its type, the chassis feels composed, and it has the kind of simple, serviceable character enthusiasts appreciate. If you want an inexpensive car with potential and don\u2019t mind a few rough edges, this one is worth a look.",
